  <div class="editable-message-body">
    <div class="comment-text editable-message-text" itemprop="commentText"><p>I&#x27;ve asked for an update from the Red Hat security team.  It looks like they did verify the vulnerability in SQLAlchemy, assigned a CVE (CVE-2012-0805), and are now working on coordinating a release.  I&#x27;ll report back when I get a date.  I know the fix is already out, but ideally I think this bug should stay private until the coordinated release for the CVE.</p>
